TESTIMONIAL_1_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: This app has been a game-changer for my fitness journey. The workout plans are tailored to my goals, and the progress tracking keeps me motivated.
TESTIMONIAL_2_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: I love how the app makes it easy to follow along with exercise videos and adjust the difficulty level. It's like having a personal trainer in my pocket.

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our fitness app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What features does the gym app offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides workout tracking, exercise guides, and progress monitoring to help you achieve your fitness goals. You can log workouts, view exercise demos, and track metrics like weight, reps, and sets.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How do I get started with the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Simply download the app, create an account, and set up your profile with your fitness details. From there, you can start logging workouts, exploring exercises, and tracking your progress.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I create custom workout routines?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, our app allows you to create and save custom workout routines tailored to your specific needs and goals. You can mix and match exercises, set target reps and weights, and schedule your routines.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Does the app offer any nutritional guidance?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: While our primary focus is on exercise tracking and workout guidance, we do offer basic nutritional information and the ability to log your daily calorie intake to support your fitness journey.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I share my progress with friends or trainers?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! Our app has built-in social features that allow you to connect with friends, share your workout logs and progress photos, and even follow your favorite trainers for motivation and tips.

ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What types of workouts are included?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app offers a wide variety of workout routines for all fitness levels, from beginner to advanced. This includes strength training, cardio, yoga, Pilates, and more.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How do I track my progress?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: You can easily log your workouts, track metrics like weight, reps, and sets, and monitor your progress over time through detailed charts and graphs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I get a personalized plan?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! Our app allows you to input your fitness goals, experience level, and preferences to generate a customized workout plan tailored just for you.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our app includes a nutrition tracker where you can log your daily food intake, get macro breakdowns, and receive personalized meal plans based on your goals.
